query:
INSERT INTO products (
  tenantId, sku, supplierCode, customerCode, description, gtin, 
  anvisaRegistry, therapeuticClass, manufacturer, unitOfMeasure, 
  unitsPerBox, category, costPrice, salePrice, minQuantity, 
  dispensingQuantity, requiresBatchControl, requiresExpiryControl, 
  requiresSerialControl, storageCondition, minTemperature, 
  maxTemperature, requiresHumidityControl, isControlledSubstance, 
  isPsychotropic, status
)
SELECT 
  60006 as tenantId, -- ID da Hapvida
  sku, supplierCode, customerCode, description, gtin, 
  anvisaRegistry, therapeuticClass, manufacturer, unitOfMeasure, 
  unitsPerBox, category, costPrice, salePrice, minQuantity, 
  dispensingQuantity, requiresBatchControl, requiresExpiryControl, 
  requiresSerialControl, storageCondition, minTemperature, 
  maxTemperature, requiresHumidityControl, isControlledSubstance, 
  isPsychotropic, status
FROM products 
WHERE sku = '401460P' 
LIMIT 1;
